"title": "8485: spiritual warfare, as conflict",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8485",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The warfare believers must fight is spiritual, personal, intense and continual. It calls for courage, determination and prayer, and therefore believers must stand in God's strength and use the armour he has provided.</p>\n<h2>General descriptions of spiritual conflict</h2>\n<h3>It is spiritual</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:12\">EPH 6:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech4:6\">ZEC 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:3-2Cor10:4\">2CO 10:3–10:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:17\">GAL 5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:11\">1PE 2:11</a></p>\n<h3>It is personal</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:31-Luke22:32\">LUK 22:31–22:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:23\">ROM 7:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:12\">2TI 3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:18\">2TI 4:18</a></p>\n<h3>It is strenuous</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:4\">HEB 12:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:33\">JHN 16:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:27-Phil1:30\">PHP 1:27–1:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:12-1Pet4:13\">1PE 4:12–4:13</a></p>\n<h3>It is continual</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:13\">EPH 6:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:3\">2TI 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:13\">HEB 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:10\">REV 12:10</a></p>\n<h2>How believers are to fight</h2>\n<h3>With courage</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:13\">1CO 16:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:9\">JOS 1:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh10:25\">JOS 10:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:6-2Chr32:8\">2CH 32:6–32:8</a></p>\n<h3>With determination</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:12\">1TI 6:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:4\">2TH 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:23\">HEB 10:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:9-1Pet5:10\">1PE 5:9–5:10</a></p>\n<h3>With watchfulness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:8\">1PE 5:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:13\">1CO 16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:1\">GAL 6:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:18\">EPH 6:18</a></p>\n<h3>With prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:18\">EPH 6:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod17:11\">EXO 17:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:13\">MAT 6:13</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:4\">LUK 11:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:41\">MAT 26:41</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:38\">MRK 14:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:46\">LUK 22:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:5\">ACT 12:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:2\">2TH 3:2</a></p>\n<h3>Standing in God's strength</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:10\">EPH 6:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:45\">1SA 17:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:40\">2SA 22:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:32-Ps18:36\">PSA 18:32–18:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:8\">PSA 118:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:16\">EPH 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:13\">PHP 4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:1\">2TI 2:1</a></p>\n<h3>Using the armour of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:11\">EPH 6:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:12-Rom13:14\">ROM 13:12–13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:4\">2CO 10:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:13-Eph6:17\">EPH 6:13–6:17</a></p>",
